CSI ...  ESC [

CSI J    clear from cursor to end of screen
CSI 1 J  clear from cursor to beginning of screen
CSI 2 J  clear entire screen and moves cursor home
CSI K    clear from cursor to EOL, cursor not changed
CSI 1 K  clear from cursor to beginning of line
CSI 2 K  clear entire line
CSI s    save cursor pos
CSI u    restore cursor pos
CSI y;xH move cursor to row y column x
CSI A    Cursor UP
CSI B    Cursor DOWN
CSI C    Cursor RIGHT
CSI D    Cursor LEFT
CSI n m  Select graphic rendition
         After CSI zero or more parameter
CSI m    is treaded as  CSI 0 m => reset
    1    bold
	 4    underline
	 7    reverse
   11-19 Alternative font (n-10)
   24    underline off
	27    inverse off
	30-37	Set foreground color 0=black   1=red  2=green 3=yellow 4=blue
	40-47	Set background color 5=magenta 6=cyan 7=white
	      combined: \e[1;31m for bold red
